@startuml SabaGroupBetting_Sequence
!theme plain
title Match Monitor Saba Group Betting - Sequence Diagram (Updated 2025-11-19)

actor "Job Scheduler" as Scheduler
participant "MatchMonitor\nController" as Controller
participant "MatchMonitorJob\nService" as JobService
participant "MMRuleSabaGB\nService" as SabaService
participant "MMRuleSabaGBProcess\nService" as ProcessService
participant "AssociationDetection\nService" as AssocService
database "MySQL\nCTS_DataCenter" as DB

note over Scheduler, DB
    **Staging Phase completed (shared with all rules)**
    **Focus on Processing Phase (Saba-specific)**
end note

Scheduler -> Controller: POST /api/matchmonitor/MatchMonitorProcessRuleSabaGroupBettingLive\nnumberOfThread=4
activate Controller

Controller -> JobService: ProcessRuleSabaGroupBetting(isLive=true, numberOfThread=4)
activate JobService

JobService -> SabaService: GetMatchRuleSabaGB(isLive=true)
activate SabaService

SabaService -> DB: EXEC CTS_DC_MatchMonitor_RuleGroupBettingSaba_Get\n@ip_LiveIndicator=1
activate DB
note right of DB
    **Returns 2 result sets:**
    1. MatchStagingList (grouped)
       - CustIDList, CTSCustIDList
       - SequenceIDList
    2. CTSCustomerList ← For mapping!
       - CustID, CTSCustID
    
    **OUT Parameter:**
    - op_MaxSequenceID
    
    **Tables:**
    - MatchMonitorStagingGroupBettingSabaLive
    - MatchMonitorRuleSetting
    - SystemParameter
end note
DB --> SabaService: MaxSequenceID, CTSCustomerList, MatchStagingList
deactivate DB

note over SabaService
    **CREATE MAPPING DICTIONARY**
    
    MappingCustDictionary = CTSCustomerList
        .Select(x => new { x.CustID, x.CTSCustID })
        .Distinct()
        .ToDictionary(x => x.CustID, x => x.CTSCustID);
    
    Example:
    { 101: 5001, 102: 5002, 103: 5003, ... }
end note

SabaService -> SabaService: Group matches by key

SabaService --> JobService: MatchStagingRuleSabaGBProcessModel\n+ MappingCustDictionary
deactivate SabaService

JobService -> JobService: Parallel process matches\nAsParallel().WithDegreeOfParallelism(4)

loop For each match (parallel)
    JobService -> ProcessService: GetInstanceProcessSabaGBService()
    activate ProcessService
    
    ProcessService -> ProcessService: PrepareProcess(matchInfo, isLive, **mappingCustDictionary**)
    note right
        **Pass MappingCustDictionary!**
        Key difference from standard GB
    end note
    
    ProcessService -> ProcessService: ProcessRound1()
    loop For each customer group
        ProcessService -> ProcessService: DetectAssociation(CTSCustIDList, CustIDList)
        note right
            **Simplified params:**
            IsDevice = true
            IsAI = true
            IsIP = true
            Is3MatchesLast7Days = true
            MappingCustDictionary = dict
        end note
        
        ProcessService -> AssocService: DetectAssociation(param)
        activate AssocService
        AssocService -> DB: Query Association Tables\n@CTSCustIds, @MappingDict
        activate DB
        DB --> AssocService: Associations with GroupID
        deactivate DB
        AssocService --> ProcessService: DetectAssociationMergeGroupEntity[]
        deactivate AssocService
        
        alt Has GroupID
            note right of ProcessService
                Process in application layer
                (No SP call for Process)
            end note
        end
    end
    
    ProcessService -> ProcessService: ProcessRound2()
    note right: Same as Round 1 with refined lists
    
    ProcessService -> ProcessService: Complete(maxSequenceID)
    note right
        Merge Round 1 and 2
        Assign GroupID
    end note
    
    alt Has Complete Matches
        ProcessService -> DB: EXEC CTS_DC_MatchMonitor_RuleGroupBettingSaba_Complete\n@ip_LiveIndicator, @ip_TransGroup
        activate DB
        note right of DB
            **Operations:**
            - INSERT/UPDATE MatchMonitorDetails
            - UPDATE MatchMonitorStagingGroupBettingSabaLive
              SET GroupID = TargetGroupID
            - INSERT MatchMonitor
            
            **Tables:**
            - MatchMonitorDetails (Reason=0)
            - MatchMonitor
            - MatchMonitorStagingGroupBettingSabaLive
        end note
        DB --> ProcessService: Success
        deactivate DB
    end
    
    ProcessService --> JobService: Complete
    deactivate ProcessService
end

JobService -> SabaService: CleanTransRuleSabaGB(isLive, maxSequenceID)
activate SabaService
SabaService -> DB: EXEC CTS_DC_MatchMonitor_RuleGroupBettingSaba_StagingClean\n@ip_LiveIndicator, @ip_MaxSequenceID
activate DB
note right of DB
    **Clean-up:**
    - DELETE old transactions
    - Keep last TimeStep
    - UPDATE SystemParameter (162/163)
    
    **Tables:**
    - MatchMonitorStagingGroupBettingSabaLive
    - SystemParameter
end note
DB --> SabaService: Deleted rows
deactivate DB
SabaService --> JobService: Success
deactivate SabaService

JobService --> Controller: true
deactivate JobService

Controller --> Scheduler: HTTP 200 OK { success: true }
deactivate Controller

note over Scheduler, DB
    **Key Saba Features Used:**
    1. ✅ MappingCustDictionary created from CTSCustomerList
    2. ✅ Fixed association criteria (no sport config)
    3. ✅ Saba-specific tables (MatchMonitorStagingGroupBettingSaba*)
    4. ✅ Results saved to MatchMonitorDetails (Reason=0)
    
    **Stored Procedures:**
    - CTS_DC_MatchMonitor_RuleGroupBettingSaba_Get
    - CTS_DC_MatchMonitor_RuleGroupBettingSaba_Complete
    - CTS_DC_MatchMonitor_RuleGroupBettingSaba_StagingClean
end note

@enduml
